This file describes how to run the testsuite of Orcc.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Prerequisites

The tests are written with DejaGnu, so you must install it for the tests to
run. DejaGnu is available for every major platform, including Windows
(in Cygwin).

Note: if DejaGnu complains that there are no global config file, just create an
empty "site.exp" file in /usr/share/dejagnu

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Testing

Just type:
  runtest

Wait for the tests to complete.
